{"TopicId":31847,"ForumId":21,"TopicTitle":"The DPRK\u0026#039;s Nuclear Bomber (Pagoe)","CreatedByName":"rryy","CreatedById":57357,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-06-07T13:04:59Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"rryy","CreatedById":57357,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-06-07T13:04:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ENORTH KEREA HAS SUCCESSFULLY DEVELOPED A NUCLEAR BOMB TO BE DROPPED FROM A PLANE. NAMED \u00C3\u00AD\u00C5\u2019\u00C5\u2019\u00C3\u00AA\u00C2\u00B4\u00C2\u00B4, OR PAGOE (MEANING \u003Cem\u003EDESTRUCTION\u003C/em\u003E*), IT CAN DESTRO -ER, DEFEND US FROM THE AMERIKAN IMPERIALISTS!\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EREADY FOR TAKEOFF:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/MUvZKwq.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022MUvZKwq.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EIN THE AIR:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/g6BZPaf.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022g6BZPaf.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ETHE BOMB HAS BEEN DROPPED:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/tlaNczh.png\u0022 alt=\u0022tlaNczh.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ENEARING DETONATION:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/iznghl2.png\u0022 alt=\u0022iznghl2.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EDETONATION:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://wallpoper.com/images/00/37/71/38/atomic-bomb_00377138.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022atomic-bomb_00377138.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EOUR PILOT \u0022SAFELY\u0022 FLYING AWAY:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/4B9KH3M.jpg\u0022 alt=\u00224B9KH3M.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EAction Groups:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E1-Release bomb\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E2-Detonates bomb\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EHow to release and detonate bomb:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E1. Get up to an altitude of 1.5 kilometer.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E2. Throttle down to 1/3 throttle and pitch up about 15-20\u00C3\u201A\u00C2\u00BA\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E3. Press \u00271\u0027 to release the bomb.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E4. To correctly detonate in midair, throttle up completely and press \u00272\u0027 when you reach 500 meters (or, of course, you can just let it hit the ground).\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E5. Quickly switch over to the plane to keep it from going out of range and safely land the pilot.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://wikisend.com/download/853944/Pagoe.craft\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:14px;\u0022\u003EDOWNLOAD\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cem\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:8px;\u0022\u003E*Google Translate was used\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222013-06-07T13:08:48Z\u0022 title=\u002206/07/2013 01:08  PM\u0022 data-short=\u002211 yr\u0022\u003EJune 7, 2013\u003C/time\u003E by rryy\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Matzenino","CreatedById":20458,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-06-07T14:47:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI love Jebediahs expression in the last picture.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EHe\u0027s like:\u0022I just committed genocide AND IT FELT GREAT!\u0022\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ENice design, but is it able to outrun interceptors?\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EA bomber isn\u0027t worth much if its shot down as soon as it enters the target area. ^^\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222013-06-07T14:49:38Z\u0022 title=\u002206/07/2013 02:49  PM\u0022 data-short=\u002211 yr\u0022\u003EJune 7, 2013\u003C/time\u003E by Matzenino\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"rryy","CreatedById":57357,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-06-07T18:41:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EOf course it can.\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#D3D3D3;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:8px;\u0022\u003E*\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cem\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#D3D3D3;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:8px;\u0022\u003E*assuming it goes at below 100 m/s\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Sun","CreatedById":66710,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-10-16T14:17:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI know it\u0027s been over a year since this thread was last active but.... this explains your signature. A lot.\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}